{"tid":2505686,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–動物也懂得耕種？","createTime":"2021-04-26T21:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T02:13:48.000Z","uid":38861,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa631b84baf3a2debf6cd1b87fd66a749ff29fa4","tid":2505686,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:25:07.000Z","msg":"耕種是人們獲取糧食的其中一道主要塗徑。<br />\n而事實上，大自然中亦有動物會使用「耕種」的方式來獲取食物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwWeo38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwWeo38.jpg&h=3af69f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)切葉蟻(Leaf‐cutter ants)就是其中一種會利用「耕種」來取得糧食的動物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yT8DQKa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyT8DQKa.jpg&h=ba505f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在熱帶樹林中，牠們約佔草食性動物的人口25%左右，每年大約會清除樹林1-2噸的草生植物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)牠們所清除的草生植物，並非是直接用於食用，而是儲存在深至地下8米的洞穴裡頭，在陰暗的環境下催迫菌類萌生在樹葉之上，而那些菌類才是牠們的真正糧食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7ZPcXy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7ZPcXy.jpg&h=374061ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牠們此舉同時間亦造就了另一道的生態平衡，把葉子的養份帶到泥土深處，使泥土更為之充滿不同礦物質，並讓其他植物的根部更容易吸收。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6yF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=2c34efd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6yF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=6830aeaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://besjournals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/1365-2435.13319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbesjournals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2F1365-2435.13319&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6yF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=d427f0bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://besjournals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/1365-2435.13319</a>"},{"pid":"c56a37935af506a75893b52904b86acd5ff901a6","tid":2505686,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:26:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">途徑</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfd94eac3e74f5869d25371d71e8e4f5cbafcab","tid":2505686,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b617afc6cfb52ef862102420f7d04545f9dc3825","tid":2505686,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T21:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fab93274143511afcef58bd42eb61b27f8cec0d","tid":2505686,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c56a37935af506a75893b52904b